						               													<description>Blitz Built Games is the card game that brings a core rule system to your favorite characters.  Use one of the four Mini Blitz decks to equip four of your Lego&amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;&amp;trade; Minifigs with Medieval, Firearms, Lasers, or Magical Equipment. &amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;We provide a unique system made to open up into any and all of your favorite genres and you provide the rest.  Bring your own characters, victory conditions, and game style.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Medieval brings sharp weapons and pointy objects to your army.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay:&amp;#10;This Mini Blitz Deck can equip four units with a total of 8 BV (Battle Value). Assign a Form/Class card to a Minifig, which defines the basic rules for a single unit, then assign Equipment cards; each assigned card provides special rules but reduces the unit's Top Speed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The scenario sets, or players agree, a Round BV. During your round, pay a unit's BV to activate it. When your Round BV is exhausted, play passes to the next player. During a unit's turn, it can Play an equipped card, Attack, or Move. Attacks are resolved by rolling 1d6 and checking the Attack Table on the equipment card, plus any special rules. Range and movement is measured in studs.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
